<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Why, Yahweh, do you stand far off?</para>

<para style="q1">Why do you hide yourself in times of trouble?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Because of their arrogance, wicked people chase the oppressed;</para>

<para style="q1">but please let the wicked be trapped by their own schemes that they have devised.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />For the wicked person boasts of his deepest desires;</para>

<para style="q1">he blesses the greedy and insults Yahweh.</para>
